  .line
    %span The way I want to test this is by
  .line
    #{form.text_field :confirmation_flow, placeholder: 'e.g. posting content to slack and seeing it show up in the invoice', required: true}
    %span.period
  .line
    %div When an error occurs,
  .line
    #{form.text_field :error_expectation, placeholder: 'e.g. I expect to see a MissingIntegrationException returned', required: true}
    %span.period

